HEADWORD: Raucity
<hw>Rau"ci*ty</hw> <pr>(r⟦add⟧"s⟦icr⟧*t⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>raucitas</ets>, from <ets>raucus</ets> hoarse: cf. F.
<ets>raucit⟦eacute⟧</ets>.]</ety> <def>Harshness of sound; rough
